#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
msgid ""
"Some OIDC providers support metadata discovery but do not return all the endpoint URLs required for the authorization code flow to complete or to support application functions, such as user logout.\n"
"To work around this limitation, you can configure the missing endpoint URL values locally, as outlined in the following example:"
